277    public PageReference createAccount() {
278        removeAccountError = false;
279        didInsertSucceed = false;
280        didTryCreate = true;
281
282        if(createAccount.RecordTypeId == null) {
283            ApexPages.addMessage(new ApexPages.Message(ApexPages.Severity.Error, System.Label.Create_Person_Record_Type_Required_MVN));
284            return null;
285        }
286
287        //Creation
288        SavePoint sp = Database.setSavePoint();
289
290        try {
291            if(!String.isBlank(createAccount.Phone)) {
292                createAccount.Phone = createAccount.Phone.replaceAll('[^0-9]', '');
293            }
294            if(!String.isBlank(createAccount.Fax)) {
295                createAccount.Fax = createAccount.Fax.replaceAll('[^0-9]', '');
296            }
297            if(createAccount.PersonEmail != null && createAccount.PersonEmail != '' && !Pattern.matches('([a-zA-Z0-9_\\-\\.]+)@((\\[a-z]{1,3}\\.[a-z]{1,3}\\.[a-z]{1,3}\\.)|(([a-zA-Z0-9\\-]+\\.)+))([a-zA-Z]{2,4}|[0-9]{1,3})', createAccount.PersonEmail)){
298                ApexPages.addMessage(new ApexPages.message(ApexPages.severity.Error, Label.Invalid_Email_Address_MVN));
299                return null;
300            }
301            
302            insert createAccount;
303            
304            createAddress.Account_GLBL__c = createAccount.Id;
305
306            if((createAddress.Name != null && !String.isBlank(createAddress.Name))
307                || (createAddress.Line_2_Adrs_Txt_GLBL__c != null && !String.isBlank(createAddress.Line_2_Adrs_Txt_GLBL__c))
308                || (createAddress.City_GLBL__c != null && !String.isBlank(createAddress.City_GLBL__c))
309                || (createAddress.St_Cd_GLBL__c != null && !String.isBlank(createAddress.St_Cd_GLBL__c))){
310                insert createAddress;
311            }
312            
313            if(!standAloneSearch){
314                if(!createReferredBy){
315                    cs.AccountId = createAccount.Id;
316                    cs.Address_GLBL__c = createAddress.Id;
317                    cs.Account_Fax_GLBL__c = createAccount.Fax;
318                    cs.Account_Phone_GLBL__c = createAccount.Phone;
319                    cs.Account_Email_GLBL__c = createAccount.PersonEmail;
320                }else{
321                    cs.Referred_By_GLBL__c = createAccount.Id;
322                }
323                
324                createReferredBy = false;
325
326                update cs;
327                getCaseValues();
328            }
329
330            clearSearch();
331            
332            didInsertSucceed = true;
333        }
334        catch (Exception e) {
335            //need to clone failed account and address records to clear id field
336            createAccount = createAccount.clone(false,true,false,false);
337            createAddress = createAddress.clone(false,true,false,false);
338            getCaseValues();
339            
340            ApexPages.addMessages(e);
341            Database.rollback(sp);
342        }
343        return null;
344    }

359    public PageReference doSearch(){
360        removeAccountError = false;
361        
362        searchAccount.FirstName = searchAccount.FirstName != null ? (searchAccount.FirstName.length() > 0 ? String.escapeSingleQuotes(searchAccount.FirstName.trim()) : '') : '';
363        searchAccount.LastName = searchAccount.LastName != null ? (searchAccount.LastName.length() > 0 ? String.escapeSingleQuotes(searchAccount.LastName.trim()) : '') : '';
364        searchAccount.Mdl_Nm_GLBL__c = searchAccount.Mdl_Nm_GLBL__c != null ? (searchAccount.Mdl_Nm_GLBL__c.length() > 0 ? String.escapeSingleQuotes(searchAccount.Mdl_Nm_GLBL__c.trim()) : '') : '';
365        searchAccount.Phone = searchAccount.Phone != null ? (searchAccount.Phone.length() > 0 ? String.escapeSingleQuotes(searchAccount.Phone.trim()) : '') : '';
366        searchAddress.City_GLBL__c = searchAddress.City_GLBL__c != null ? (searchAddress.City_GLBL__c.length() > 0 ? String.escapeSingleQuotes(searchAddress.City_GLBL__c.trim()) : '') : '';
367        searchAddress.Zip_Postal_Code_GLBL__c = searchAddress.Zip_Postal_Code_GLBL__c != null ? (searchAddress.Zip_Postal_Code_GLBL__c.length() > 0 ? String.escapeSingleQuotes(searchAddress.Zip_Postal_Code_GLBL__c.trim()) : '') : '';
368        
369        searchResults = new List<PersonSearchResultMockMVN>();
370        
371        //Make sure something is filled out
372        didTryCreate = false;
373        if (String.isBlank(searchAccount.FirstName) && String.isBlank(searchAccount.LastName) && String.isBlank(searchAccount.Mdl_Nm_GLBL__c) && String.isBlank(searchAccount.Phone) && String.isBlank(searchAddress.City_GLBL__c) && String.isBlank(searchAddress.St_Cd_GLBL__c) && String.isBlank(searchAddress.Zip_Postal_Code_GLBL__c)) {
374            ApexPages.addMessage(new ApexPages.Message(ApexPages.Severity.Info, System.Label.Search_Term_Required_MVN));
375            return null;
376        }
377
378        //Pick search path: Only Accounts, Addresses, SOSL Phone
379        if (!String.isBlank(searchAccount.Phone)) {
380            searchResults = buildPhoneSearchResults();
381        } else if (String.isBlank(searchAddress.City_GLBL__c) && String.isBlank(searchAddress.St_Cd_GLBL__c) && String.isBlank(searchAddress.Zip_Postal_Code_GLBL__c)) {
382            searchResults = buildAccountSearchResults();
383        } else {
384            searchResults = buildAddressSearchResults();
385        }
386
387        if(searchResults == null) {
388            searchResults = new List<PersonSearchResultMockMVN>();
389            return null;
390        }
391
392        if (searchResults.size() >= SEARCHLIMIT) {
393            searchResults = new List<PersonSearchResultMockMVN>();
394            ApexPages.addMessage(new ApexPages.Message(ApexPages.Severity.Info, System.Label.Too_Many_Results_MVN));
395        } else if (searchResults.size() == 0 ) {
396            searchResults = new List<PersonSearchResultMockMVN>();
397            ApexPages.addMessage(new ApexPages.Message(ApexPages.Severity.Info, System.Label.No_Search_Results_MVN));
398        }
399
400        if(searchResults == null) searchResults = new List<PersonSearchResultMockMVN>();
401        didSearch = true;
402        showNewButton = true;
403        return null;
404    }

406    public List<PersonSearchResultMockMVN> buildAddressSearchResults() {
407        List<PersonSearchResultMockMVN> resultList = new List<PersonSearchResultMockMVN>();
408        String qString = 'SELECT ' + ADDRESSFIELDS;
409        qString += ' FROM Address_GLBL__c ' + buildAddressWhereClause() + ADDRESSORDERBY + ' LIMIT ' + SEARCHLIMIT;
410
411        List<Address_GLBL__c> addressList = database.query(qString);
412        for(Address_GLBL__c a : addressList) {
413                Account acct = new Account(Id = a.Account_GLBL__c);
414                acct.FirstName = a.Account_GLBL__r.FirstName;
415                acct.LastName = a.Account_GLBL__r.LastName;
416                acct.Mdl_Nm_GLBL__c = a.Account_GLBL__r.Mdl_Nm_GLBL__c;
417                acct.RecordTypeId = a.Account_GLBL__r.RecordTypeId;
418    
419                resultList.add(new PersonSearchResultMockMVN(acct,a));
420        }
421        
422        return resultList;
423    }

425    public List<PersonSearchResultMockMVN> buildAccountSearchResults() {
426        List<PersonSearchResultMockMVN> resultList = new List<PersonSearchResultMockMVN>();
427
428        String qString = 'SELECT ' + ACCOUNTFIELDS;
429        qString += ',(SELECT ' + ADDRESSFIELDS + ' FROM Addresses_GLBL__r)';
430        qString += ' FROM Account ' + buildAccountWhereClause() + ACCOUNTORDERBY + ' LIMIT ' + SEARCHLIMIT;
431        system.debug(qString);
432        system.debug(validRecordTypeIds);
433        String translatedCountryValue = null;
434        if(searchAddress.Adrs_Cntry_Cd_GLBL__c != null && searchAddress.Adrs_Cntry_Cd_GLBL__c != ''){
435            for(Schema.PicklistEntry countryPicklistVal:Schema.sObjectType.Address_GLBL__c.fields.Adrs_Cntry_Cd_GLBL__c.getPicklistValues()){
436                if(countryPicklistVal.getValue() == searchAddress.Adrs_Cntry_Cd_GLBL__c){
437                    translatedCountryValue = countryPicklistVal.getLabel();
438                }
439            }
440        }
441        
442        List<Account> accountList = database.query(qString);
443        for(Account a : accountList ) {
444            if(a.Addresses_GLBL__r.size() > 0) {
445                for(Address_GLBL__c addr : a.Addresses_GLBL__r) {
446                    if(translatedCountryValue != null &&
447                        translatedCountryValue != addr.Adrs_Cntry_Cd_GLBL__c){
448                        continue;
449                    }
450                    resultList.add(new PersonSearchResultMockMVN(a,addr));
451                }
452            } else {
453                resultList.add(new PersonSearchResultMockMVN(a));
454            }
455        }
456
457        return resultList;
458    }

460    public List<PersonSearchResultMockMVN> buildPhoneSearchResults () {
461
462        //Do initial query
463        String queryString = buildSOSLString();
464        if(queryString == null) {
465            return null;
466        }
467
468        LIST<LIST<SObject>> soslResult;
469        try {
470            system.debug('>>>>>>> ' + queryString);
471            soslResult = search.query(queryString);
472        } catch (exception e) {
473            ApexPages.addMessage(new ApexPages.Message(ApexPages.Severity.Info, e.getMessage()));
474            return null;
475        }
476
477        //Set up Maps and lists needed
478        LIST<LIST<SObject>> results = soslResult;
479        List<Account> acctResults = new List<Account>();
480        List<Address_GLBL__c> addrResults = new List<Address_GLBL__c>();
481        //AccountId_AddressId to the Mock Result
482        Map<String,PersonSearchResultMockMVN> uResults = new Map<String,PersonSearchResultMockMVN>();
483        
484        Map<Id,Account> acctIds = new Map<Id,Account>();
485
486        //Separate out what kind each list is
487        for(List<SObject> oneKind : results) {
488            if(oneKind.size() > 0) {
489                String typeId = oneKind[0].Id;
490                if(typeId.startsWith(acctPrefix)) {
491                    acctResults = (List<Account>) oneKind;
492                } else if(typeId.startsWith(addrPrefix)) {
493                    addrResults = (List<Address_GLBL__c>) oneKind;
494                }
495            }
496        }
497
498        //Get related Addresses
499        for(Account a : acctResults) {
500            acctIds.put(a.Id,a);
501            if (String.isBlank(searchAddress.City_GLBL__c) && String.isBlank(searchAddress.St_Cd_GLBL__c) && String.isBlank(searchAddress.Zip_Postal_Code_GLBL__c)) {
502                uResults.put(a.Id,new PersonSearchResultMockMVN(a));
503            }
504        }
505
506        Set<Id> idSet = acctIds.keySet();
507        String qString = 'SELECT ' + ADDRESSFIELDS + ' FROM Address_GLBL__c ' + buildAddressWhereClause() + ' AND Account_GLBL__c in :idSet' + ADDRESSORDERBY + ' LIMIT ' + SEARCHLIMIT;
508        List<Address_GLBL__c> subAddrs = database.query(qString);
509        addrResults.addAll(subAddrs);
510
511        for(Address_GLBL__c addr : addrResults) {
512            Account acct = new Account(Id = addr.Account_GLBL__c);
513            acct.FirstName = addr.Account_GLBL__r.FirstName;
514            acct.LastName = addr.Account_GLBL__r.LastName;
515            acct.Mdl_Nm_GLBL__c = addr.Account_GLBL__r.Mdl_Nm_GLBL__c;
516            acct.RecordTypeId = addr.Account_GLBL__r.RecordTypeId;
517
518            String key = acct.Id + '_' + addr.Id;
519            if (!uResults.containsKey(key)) {
520                if(uResults.containsKey(acct.Id)) {
521                    PersonSearchResultMockMVN psr = uResults.remove(acct.Id);
522                    psr.setAddress(addr);
523                    uResults.put(key,psr);
524                } else {
525                    uResults.put(key,new PersonSearchResultMockMVN(acct,addr));
526                }
527            }
528        }
529
530        return uResults.values();
531    }
532
533    public String buildSOSLString(){
534        //Put together final query and error check it
535        String qString = 'FIND {';
536        String findString = '';
537
538        //Cannot search for phone numbers with punctuation
539        findString = searchAccount.Phone.replaceAll('[^0-9]', '');
540        if (findString.length() < 2) {
541            ApexPages.addMessage(new ApexPages.Message(ApexPages.Severity.Info, System.Label.SOSL_Phone_Search_Min_Char_MVN + ' ' + findString));
542            return null;
543        }

22    public static List<Case> createRequests(List<Case> interactions, String status){
23         List<Case> requests = new List<Case>();
24         for (Case c : interactions) {
25             Case request = c.clone(false);
26             request.ParentId = c.id;
27             request.Status = status;
28             
29             requests.add(request);
30             requests.add(request.clone(false));
31         }
32         insert requests;
33        
34         return requests;
35    }
